Specifically, the EZVIZ Image-Encryption video decryption in
`scripts/ezviz_decrypt.py` (and its eventual home in the integration) is an
independent implementation whose algorithm is derived from
`pyezvizapi.stream.decrypt_hikvision_ps_video`. pyEzvizApi is used only as a
development/test dependency (a decryption oracle); it is NOT a runtime dependency.
